Class LocalTimeTextField

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.scene.control.Skinnable

    public class LocalTimeTextField
extends CalendarTimeTextField
    LocalTime (JSR-310) text field component. This is an extension of the CalendarTimeTextField adding the new date API JSR-310. Since Calendar will not be removed from the JDK, too many applications use it, this approach of extending CalendarTextField is the most flexible one.
